    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1893-11-09T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1893-11-09T00:00:00-05:00" n="187"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d187">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Young</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Gresham</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States,<lb/>Guatemala and
                                Honduras</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">La Libertad</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1893-11-09">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 9, 1893</hi>
                        </date>. (Received November 10.)</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Have demanded to be informed if Honduras Government authorized firing on the <hi
                        rend="italic">Costa Rica</hi>. Am here on <hi rend="italic">Alliance</hi>
                    waiting reply. Had I authority would make short work of this matter. I await
                    your instructions.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Young</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
